	<article class="post-154257 post type-post status-publish hentry category-the-conversation tag-alinsky-saul tag-brooks-david tag-collins-gail tag-gentrification tag-new-york-state tag-obama-barack tag-united-states-international-relations per-alinsky-saul per-brooks-david per-collins-gail per-obama-barack des-gentrification des-united-states-international-relations geo-new-york-state news_keywords-barack-obama-2 news_keywords-david-brooks news_keywords-gail-collins news_keywords-gentrification news_keywords-new-york news_keywords-saul-alinsky news_keywords-us-foreign-policy" id="post-154257">
	<header class="postHeader">
				<div class="postKicker">
			<span class="kicker"><a href="//opinionator.blogs.nytimes.com/category/the-conversation/?module=BlogCategory&version=Blog Post&action=Click&contentCollection=Opinion&pgtype=Blogs&region=Header">The Conversation</a></span>
